{
  "stateName": "Uttar Pradesh",
  "documentType": "driving_licence",
  "commonIssues": "<div class=\"accordion\" id=\"issuesAccordion\">\\n    <div class=\"card mb-2\">\\n        <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading1\">\\n            <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\\n                <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left\" type=\"button\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"\\n                    data-target=\"#collapse1\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Documentation & E-KYC Errors\\n                </button>\\n            </h5>\\n        </div>\\n        <div id=\"collapse1\" class=\"collapse show\" data-parent=\"#issuesAccordion\">\\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\\n                <p>Rejection due to name/address mismatches, blurry documents, biometric mismatch, or incorrect vehicle class selection.</p>\\n                <p><strong>How to fix:</strong> Use Aadhaar-based E-KYC authentication. Ensure your Aadhaar biometric details are updated at a local center first if fingerprints fail. Double-check 'Vehicle Class' before applying, as it cannot be changed later without a new application.</p>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\"card mb-2\">\\n        <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading2\">\\n            <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\\n                <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"\\n                    data-target=\"#collapse2\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Failed Driving Tests on Automated Tracks\\n                </button>\\n            </h5>\\n        </div>\\n        <div id=\"collapse2\" class=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#issuesAccordion\">\\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\\n                <p>Inability to pass tests on automated tracks due to strict sensor evaluations.</p>\\n                <p><strong>How to fix:</strong> Familiarize yourself with the specific track layout (often Figure-8 and Reverse-S). Practice clutch control extensively, as sensors penalize stalling or rolling back on inclines.</p>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\"card mb-2\">\\n        <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading3\">\\n            <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\\n                <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"\\n                    data-target=\"#collapse3\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Long Delays & Unpaid Challan Blocks\\n                </button>\\n            </h5>\\n        </div>\\n        <div id=\"collapse3\" class=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#issuesAccordion\">\\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\\n                <p>Significant delays in receiving licenses, long waiting times for slots, and suspensions blocking renewals due to unpaid traffic fines.</p>\\n                <p><strong>How to fix:</strong> Clear all pending e-challans on your vehicle and name before applying for ANY DL service, as the Parivahan portal will auto-block applications until fines are paid. Check slot availability exactly at midnight.</p>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\"card mb-2\">\\n        <div class=\"card-header\" id=\"heading4\">\\n            <h5 class=\"mb-0\">\\n                <button class=\"btn btn-link text-left collapsed\" data-toggle=\"collapse\"\\n                    data-target=\"#collapse4\" style=\"white-space: normal; word-break: break-word;\">\\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chevron-right mr-2\"></i>Agent Dependence and Fraud\\n                </button>\\n            </h5>\\n        </div>\\n        <div id=\"collapse4\" class=\"collapse\" data-parent=\"#issuesAccordion\">\\n            <div class=\"card-body\">\\n                <p>Reliance on agents leading to issues with official documentation and overcharging.</p>\\n                <p><strong>How to fix:</strong> UP RTOs have transitioned to \"Faceless\" online services. Do not hand over original documents to unauthorized agents. Apply directly via Sarathi to ensure authentic payment receipts.</p>\\n            </div>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n</div>"
}
